graph LR
    RHODS[RHODS Operator]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    RHODS -->|orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.24+<br/>REQUIRED]
    RHODS -->|platform| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.12+<br/>REQUIRED for RHOAI]
    RHODS -->|webhook certs| CertMgr[Cert Manager /<br/>OpenShift Service CA<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    RHODS -.->|monitoring| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.68+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    RHODS -.->|service mesh| Istio[Istio / Service Mesh 2.4+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    RHODS -.->|serverless| Knative[Knative / Serverless 1.30+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    RHODS -.->|observability| RHOBS[RHOBS Monitoring Stack<br/>OPTIONAL - RHOAI]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Components Deployed
    RHODS -->|deploys| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    RHODS -->|deploys| KServe[KServe Operator]
    RHODS -->|deploys| Pipelines[Kubeflow Pipelines]
    RHODS -->|deploys| ModelRegistry[Model Registry Operator]
    RHODS -->|deploys| NotebookCtrl[Notebook Controller]
    RHODS -->|deploys| RayOp[Ray Operator]
    RHODS -->|deploys| TrainingOp[Training Operator]
    RHODS -->|deploys| FeastOp[Feast Operator]
    RHODS -->|deploys| MLflowOp[MLflow Operator]
    RHODS -->|deploys| TrustyAI[TrustyAI Operator]
    RHODS -->|deploys| Kueue[Kueue]
    RHODS -->|deploys| Trainer[Trainer]
    RHODS -->|deploys| LlamaStack[LlamaStack Operator]
    RHODS -->|deploys| ModelsAsService[Models as Service]

    %% Infrastructure Services Configured
    RHODS -->|configures| MonStack[Monitoring Stack<br/>Prometheus, AlertManager, Grafana]
    RHODS -->|configures| AuthSvc[Auth Service]
    RHODS -->|configures| Gateway[API Gateway]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|uses| K8s
    KServe -->|integrates| Istio
    KServe -->|integrates| Knative
    Pipelines -->|uses| K8s
    NotebookCtrl -->|uses| K8s
    MonStack -->|integrates| PrometheusOp

    %% External Services
    RHODS -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    RHODS -->|fetches manifests| GitRepos[Component Git Repos<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    RHODS -->|pulls images| Registry[Container Registries<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    RHODS -->|auth integration| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

